Corvus Systems Inc said itnamed Lewis Lipton its president and chief operating officer.    Lipton had been consulting for Corvus for the past ninemonths and prior to that was the chief executive officer ofTrimedia Corp.    He reports to James Siehl, who had been acting as presidentand continues as chief executive officer. Siehl was also namedChairman of the Board, which he had also been acting as. Reuter&#3;